data.title: 500 Topics for Debates and Argumentative Essays
data.meta_description: Search 500 classroom debate and argumentative essay topics, categorized by age and subject. Complete with background info and starter prompts.
data.text:
Dive right into a deep discussion with Topic Templates!

Browse Kialo’s extensive library of classroom debate and argumentative essay topics. Each template comes with background info and prompts, so you can get discussing straight away!

An illustrated teacher sits thinking at their desk as discussion cards, and pro and con claims float around their head. The pro claim is “Macbeth’s fate was fixed by the witches’ prophecy.” and the con claim is “Macbeth’s own hubris caused his demise.” An illustrated teacher sits thinking at their desk as discussion cards, and pro and con claims float around their head.
